3 events:
onmousedown
onmousemove
onmouseup
* first mouse then toach
user pressed canvas - 
onmousedown(ev) = change  

gismouselicked= true (before:False)
get ev.offsetwidth ev.offsetheight
onmouseup = change gvar to False

onmousemove(ev):
- compare clicked spot with the lines curr Position
- if it matches where the user clicked change selecetdcurrlineIDX
- get ev.offsetwidth ev.offsetheight
- change the position of seleceted line
- !!! works only while gismouselicked= true

